Was able to implement this using a global event listener :tada:

```
/* Listen for all messages */
window.addEventListener('message', event =&gt; {

	/* If the message is a HubSpot Form, yippy! */
	if (event.data.type === 'hsFormCallback' &amp;&amp; event.data.eventName === 'onFormReady') {

		/* Let's find out if we should apply BV to this particular form */
		bvChecker(event);
	}
});
```
